---
import PrimaryButton from './PrimaryButton.astro';
---


<div class="wrapper">
<div class="process center spacing">
    <h3 class="section-title">The Game Plan</h3>
    <p class="process-paragraph">IT'S EASY TO LOOK AWESOME!
</div>

<div class=container-gameplan>
  <article class="gameplan-card center">
    <div class="face gameplan1">
      <div class=content-gameplan>
        <img  alt="schedule a professional headshot, lancaster photographer, lancaster headshots,business headshots near me" height=75
          src=https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/50f79c6fe4b00d3480c9bbf0/1577471673312-256TTZOWDOXBV99W5BFK/Calendar-1+%28optimized%29.png?content-type=image%2Fpng loading="lazy" width=75>
         
          <span class="spacing">SCHEDULE</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="face gameplan2">
      <div class=content-gameplan>
        <p>Give the <b>SCHEDULE</b> button a tap!</p>
        <p>Select an appointment that works best for you.</p>
        <PrimaryButton text="SCHEDULE" url="/rates"  />
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="gameplan-card center">
    <div class="face gameplan1">
      <div class=content-gameplan>
        <img alt="professional headshot pictures, professional photography, lancaster pa headshots" height=75
         src=https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/50f79c6fe4b00d3480c9bbf0/1593027627807-UEKQXEIKT61WFJQI48EP/Camera+%28optimized%29.png?content-type=image%2Fpng loading="lazy" width=75>
          
          <span class="spacing">SHOOT</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="face gameplan2">
      <div class=content-gameplan>
        <p>It's fun and easy!<br>I will guide you into pictures that will propel your career.</p>
        <PrimaryButton text="SCHEDULE" url="/rates"  />
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="gameplan-card center">
    <div class="face gameplan1">
      <div class=content-gameplan>
        <img  alt="company headshots, linkedin headshots, social media headshots, headshot photographers, professional headshots near me" height=75
          src=https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/50f79c6fe4b00d3480c9bbf0/1593027096649-E21ID0886HMI4H62JU77/share_PNG19%28optimized%29.png?content-type=image%2Fpng loading="lazy" width=75>
          
          <span class="spacing">SHARE</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="face gameplan2">
      <div class=content-gameplan>
        <p>Share your images with everyone!<br> Stand out and be recognized as an expert in your field.</p>
        <PrimaryButton text="SCHEDULE" url="/rates"  />
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
</div>

<style>

/*benefits-3 & Gameplan*/
.gameplan-card .face {
  width: min(370px, 100%);
  margin-inline:auto;
  height: 200px;
  transition: 0.5s;
  text-align: center;
 
}
.container-gameplan,
.gameplan-card .face.gameplan1 {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
   
}



.container-gameplan {
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-items: center;


}

.gameplan-card {
  position: relative;
}


.gameplan-card .face.gameplan1 {
  position: relative;
  background-color: var(--drkbg);
  justify-content: center;
  z-index: 1;
  transform: translateY(100px);
}


.gameplan-card:hover .face.gameplan1 {
  background: var(--drkbg);
  transform: translateY(0);
}
.face.gameplan1 .content-gameplan {
  opacity: 0.75;
  transition: 0.5s;
  line-height: 1;
}
.gameplan-card:hover .face.gameplan1 .content-gameplan {
  opacity: 1;
}
.content-gameplan img {
  max-height: 100px;
  filter: invert(100%);
  margin-inline: auto;
}


.gameplan-card span {
    font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
    color: var(--ltclr);
    margin: 0;
    margin-top: var(--size-5);
  
  }



.container-gameplan .gameplan-card .face.gameplan2 {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

.gameplan-card .face.gameplan2 {
  position: relative;
  padding: var(--size-4);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  transform: translateY(-100px);
}

.gameplan-card:hover .face.gameplan2 {
  transform: translateY(0);
}
.content-gameplan p {
  font-family: var(--ff-secondary);
  color: var(--blkclr);
  font-size: var(--fs-400);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
}
.content-gameplan {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--size-3);
}
@media screen and (min-width: 641px) {
  .container-gameplan {
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-around;
    padding-inline:var(--size-12);
  }
}

/*process styles*/
.process-paragraph {
  font-size: var(--fs-450);
  text-align: center;
  letter-spacing: var(--ltr-space);
  padding-bottom:var(--size-7);
}

.content-gameplan :global(.primary-btn) {
    font-size: var(--fs-350);
    padding: var(--size-3) var(--size-8);
    margin-top:var(--size-3);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
    .content-gameplan :global(.primary-btn) {
      font-size: var(--fs-300);
    }
  }




</style>
